{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01S4jJADoA6VvzwLJ6LYUDJd","type":"tool_result","content":"50\t  readonly errorCategory?: import('../agents/types.js').ErrorCategory;\n51\t}\n52\t\n53\t/** Discriminated union of all stream events the parser can emit. */\n54\texport type StreamEvent =\n55\t  | ToolStartEvent\n56\t  | ToolInputEvent\n57\t  | ToolCompleteEvent\n58\t  | TextEvent\n59\t  | RetryEvent\n60\t  | ResultEvent;\n61\t\n62\t// --- Parser ---\n63\t\n64\t/**\n65\t * Parse a single NDJSON line from Claude's stream-json output.\n66\t *\n67\t * Returns a typed StreamEvent for recognized events, or null for:\n68\t * - Invalid JSON\n69\t * - Empty/whitespace lines"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_011KW5B7oWpj1MKDHqa2H54S","session_id":"74f4684f-cc80-4828-8405-943cba326449","uuid":"e1e67f1d-0496-47a9-941f-a5fa09bb12e0","timestamp":"2026-04-03T21:45:41.826Z"}
