{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01ErKJFsAPwg6qN5N4JEv5rR","type":"tool_result","content":"50\t\n51\t**Result: PASS**\n52\t\n53\t- Test: \"retries up to 3 times with test failure context\" — passed (verified 2 git resets between 3 attempts)\n54\t- Test: \"retry prompt includes previous test failure output\" — passed (second dispatch contains \"Previous attempt failed tests\" and \"TypeError at line 42\")\n55\t- Test: \"includes test failure output on retry (AC #5)\" — passed\n56\t\n57\t### AC #6: Escalation after 3 failed attempts\n58\t\n59\t**Result: PASS**\n60\t\n61\t- Test: \"returns escalated after 3 consecutive failures\" — passed (resolved=false, attempts=3, escalated=true)\n62\t- Test: \"escalation message contains worktree path, branch, files, and git diff command\" — passed\n63\t- Escalation message includes: worktree path (`/repo`), branch name, conflicting files, `git diff` command\n64\t\n65\t### AC #7: ConflictResolutionResult interface shape\n66\t\n67\t**Result: PASS**\n68\t\n69\t- Interface at line 48 includes: `resolved: boolean`, `attempts: number`, `escalated: boolean`, `escalationMessage?: string`, `testResults?: { passed: number; failed: number; coverage?: number }`, `resolvedFiles?: string[]`\n70\t- Test: \"success result has correct shape\" — passed\n71\t- Test: \"escalated result has correct shape\" — passed\n72\t\n73\t### AC #8: Driver dispatch prompt includes all required context\n74\t\n75\t**Result: PASS**\n76\t\n77\t- Test: \"dispatches driver with correct prompt containing conflict markers (AC #2, #8)\" — passed\n78\t- Test: \"includes main and branch descriptions (AC #8)\" — passed\n79\t- Test: \"includes instructions to resolve and commit (AC #8)\" — passed\n80\t- Prompt contains: (a) conflicting files with conflict-marker content, (b) main branch description, (c) feature branch description, (d) instructions to resolve preserving both changes\n81\t\n82\t### AC #9: MergeConflictContext interface shape\n83\t\n84\t**Result: PASS**\n85\t\n86\t- Interface at line 26 includes: `epicId: string`, `branch: string`, `conflicts: string[]`, `mainDescription: string`, `branchDescription: string`, `cwd: string`, `testCommand: string`, `driver: AgentDriver`\n87\t- Test: \"has all required fields\" — passed\n88\t\n89\t### AC #10: onConflict callback on mergeWorktree\n90\t\n91\t**Result: PASS**\n92\t\n93\t- `OnConflictCallback` type exported from `worktree-manager.ts` (line 129)\n94\t- `mergeWorktree` signature includes `onConflict?: OnConflictCallback` (line 291)\n95\t- Test: \"invokes onConflict callback when conflicts detected and callback provided\" — passed\n96\t- Test: \"does NOT invoke onConflict when no conflicts detected\" — passed\n97\t- Test: \"preserves existing behavior when onConflict is NOT provided\" — passed\n98\t- Test: \"returns conflict result when onConflict returns escalated\" — passed\n99\t- Test: \"passes conflict context to onConflict callback\" — passed\n100\t\n101\t## Test Evidence\n102\t\n103\tAll 30 merge-agent tests passed. All 5 onConflict worktree-manager tests passed.\n104\t\n105\t### merge-agent.test.ts (30 tests)\n106\t\n107\t- MergeConflictContext interface shape (AC #9): 1 test\n108\t- ConflictResolutionResult interface shape (AC #7): 2 tests\n109\t- buildConflictPrompt (AC #2, #8): 6 tests\n110\t- resolveConflicts exports (AC #1): 1 test\n111\t- resolveConflicts empty conflicts guard: 1 test\n112\t- resolveConflicts successful resolution (AC #3, #4): 3 tests\n113\t- resolveConflicts retry on test failure (AC #5): 2 tests\n114\t- resolveConflicts escalation after 3 failures (AC #6): 2 tests\n115\t- resolveConflicts unparseable test output: 1 test\n116\t- resolveConflicts driver dispatch failure: 3 tests\n117\t- resolveConflicts test command failure edge cases: 2 tests\n118\t- resolveConflicts git reset failure during retry: 1 test\n119\t\n120\t### worktree-manager.test.ts (5 onConflict tests)\n121\t\n122\t- invokes onConflict callback when conflicts detected and callback provided\n123\t- does NOT invoke onConflict when no conflicts detected\n124\t- preserves existing behavior when onConflict is NOT provided\n125\t- returns conflict result when onConflict returns escalated\n126\t- passes conflict context to onConflict callback\n127\t\n128\t## Files\n129\t\n130\t| File | Action |\n131\t|------|--------|\n132\t| `src/lib/merge-agent.ts` | Created (252 lines) |\n133\t| `src/lib/__tests__/merge-agent.test.ts` | Created (525 lines) |\n134\t| `src/lib/worktree-manager.ts` | Modified (added OnConflictCallback type, onConflict parameter) |\n135\t| `src/lib/__tests__/worktree-manager.test.ts` | Modified (added 5 onConflict tests) |\n136\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"74f4684f-cc80-4828-8405-943cba326449","uuid":"e51c0ac2-378d-4c37-bd3f-0de3b98e933b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T22:01:38.410Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/verification/18-2-merge-agent-conflict-resolution-proof.md","content":"\n**Result: PASS**\n\n- Test: \"retries up to 3 times with test failure context\" — passed (verified 2 git resets between 3 attempts)\n- Test: \"retry prompt includes previous test failure output\" — passed (second dispatch contains \"Previous attempt failed tests\" and \"TypeError at line 42\")\n- Test: \"includes test failure output on retry (AC #5)\" — passed\n\n### AC #6: Escalation after 3 failed attempts\n\n**Result: PASS**\n\n- Test: \"returns escalated after 3 consecutive failures\" — passed (resolved=false, attempts=3, escalated=true)\n- Test: \"escalation message contains worktree path, branch, files, and git diff command\" — passed\n- Escalation message includes: worktree path (`/repo`), branch name, conflicting files, `git diff` command\n\n### AC #7: ConflictResolutionResult interface shape\n\n**Result: PASS**\n\n- Interface at line 48 includes: `resolved: boolean`, `attempts: number`, `escalated: boolean`, `escalationMessage?: string`, `testResults?: { passed: number; failed: number; coverage?: number }`, `resolvedFiles?: string[]`\n- Test: \"success result has correct shape\" — passed\n- Test: \"escalated result has correct shape\" — passed\n\n### AC #8: Driver dispatch prompt includes all required context\n\n**Result: PASS**\n\n- Test: \"dispatches driver with correct prompt containing conflict markers (AC #2, #8)\" — passed\n- Test: \"includes main and branch descriptions (AC #8)\" — passed\n- Test: \"includes instructions to resolve and commit (AC #8)\" — passed\n- Prompt contains: (a) conflicting files with conflict-marker content, (b) main branch description, (c) feature branch description, (d) instructions to resolve preserving both changes\n\n### AC #9: MergeConflictContext interface shape\n\n**Result: PASS**\n\n- Interface at line 26 includes: `epicId: string`, `branch: string`, `conflicts: string[]`, `mainDescription: string`, `branchDescription: string`, `cwd: string`, `testCommand: string`, `driver: AgentDriver`\n- Test: \"has all required fields\" — passed\n\n### AC #10: onConflict callback on mergeWorktree\n\n**Result: PASS**\n\n- `OnConflictCallback` type exported from `worktree-manager.ts` (line 129)\n- `mergeWorktree` signature includes `onConflict?: OnConflictCallback` (line 291)\n- Test: \"invokes onConflict callback when conflicts detected and callback provided\" — passed\n- Test: \"does NOT invoke onConflict when no conflicts detected\" — passed\n- Test: \"preserves existing behavior when onConflict is NOT provided\" — passed\n- Test: \"returns conflict result when onConflict returns escalated\" — passed\n- Test: \"passes conflict context to onConflict callback\" — passed\n\n## Test Evidence\n\nAll 30 merge-agent tests passed. All 5 onConflict worktree-manager tests passed.\n\n### merge-agent.test.ts (30 tests)\n\n- MergeConflictContext interface shape (AC #9): 1 test\n- ConflictResolutionResult interface shape (AC #7): 2 tests\n- buildConflictPrompt (AC #2, #8): 6 tests\n- resolveConflicts exports (AC #1): 1 test\n- resolveConflicts empty conflicts guard: 1 test\n- resolveConflicts successful resolution (AC #3, #4): 3 tests\n- resolveConflicts retry on test failure (AC #5): 2 tests\n- resolveConflicts escalation after 3 failures (AC #6): 2 tests\n- resolveConflicts unparseable test output: 1 test\n- resolveConflicts driver dispatch failure: 3 tests\n- resolveConflicts test command failure edge cases: 2 tests\n- resolveConflicts git reset failure during retry: 1 test\n\n### worktree-manager.test.ts (5 onConflict tests)\n\n- invokes onConflict callback when conflicts detected and callback provided\n- does NOT invoke onConflict when no conflicts detected\n- preserves existing behavior when onConflict is NOT provided\n- returns conflict result when onConflict returns escalated\n- passes conflict context to onConflict callback\n\n## Files\n\n| File | Action |\n|------|--------|\n| `src/lib/merge-agent.ts` | Created (252 lines) |\n| `src/lib/__tests__/merge-agent.test.ts` | Created (525 lines) |\n| `src/lib/worktree-manager.ts` | Modified (added OnConflictCallback type, onConflict parameter) |\n| `src/lib/__tests__/worktree-manager.test.ts` | Modified (added 5 onConflict tests) |\n","numLines":87,"startLine":50,"totalLines":136}}}
